text: Dóra Bodonyi (born 7 November 1993) is a Hungarian sprint canoeist. She participated at the 2018 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships, winning a medal.K-1 1000 m results ==References== Category:Living people Category:1993 births Category:Hungarian female canoeists Category:ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships medalists in kayak Category:European Games competitors for Hungary Category:Canoeists at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games medalists in canoeing Category:European Games silver medalists for Hungary
